                </div>
                <div style="clear:both"></div>
				<div class="entry">
					<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/עדכון-בלוג-200512-page-001.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5107" title="עדכון בלוג - 200512-page-001" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/עדכון-בלוג-200512-page-001.jpg" alt="" width="521" height="961" /></a></p>
